Supporting information Additional Supporting Information may be found in the online version of this article: Appendix S1 Methods. 
Tables S1 and S2 For each seizure parameter that was affected by CBDV + AED treatment, the analysis of the individual AED effect is given (either as ANOVA or Chi-squared). 
The directions of significant effects are also given by an upward or downward arrow (irrespective of the parameter, all significant AED effects described are anticonvulsant). 
Additionally, the doses at which AEDs were significantly anticonvulsant are indicated with post hoc p values given after. 
Finally, analyses of interactions between CBDV and AED effects are given. 
